Vowing to continue his legacy. That's the pledge from many fellow musicians who spoke at rapper Riky Rick's memorial service in Johannesburg. eNCA's Masego Rahlaga was at his memorial service. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A tribute walk will be held at one of the late South African rapper, Rikhado Makhado’s favourite hangouts in Braamfontein. The 34-year-old artist and fashionista, also known as Riky Rick, passed away last Wednesday. WATCH: Memorial service for the late rapper Riky Rick An intimate funeral service with close friends and family took place earlier this week. Many fellow musicians who spoke at the memorial service at the Wanderers Stadium in Johannesburg vowed to continue his legacy. His death sent shock waves around the country, with many taking to social media to express their grief.